BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:Adam Faucett // T.V. Mike
DTSTART;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260415T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Indiana/Indianapolis:20260415T210000
UID:ai1ec-148318-94887@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Doors at 6:30pmLittle-Rock-born singer-songwriter Adam Faucett
  carries a voice “that knocks your brain into the back of your skull” 
 (The Onion A.V. Club) and a catalog of swamp-soaked folk\, blues\, and cos
 mic Americana that has landed him on stages with the likes of Jason Isbell
 \, Lucero\, King Buzzo and Weedeater.Since going solo in 2006\, he has rel
 eased six critically praised albums—most recently New Variations of the 
 Reaper (Last Chance Records\, Sept. 2025)—and toured relentlessly across
  the U.S. and Europe\, earning spots on American Songwriter’s “Top 50 
 Albums of the Year” and PopMatters’ “Top 20 Americana Albums.” His
  Arkansas-gothic narratives\, keening and wailed\, make any spot feel genu
 inely present\, but somehow timeless.
LOCATION:Orbit Room\, 107 North College Avenue\, Suite 001\, Bloomington
URL:https://wfhb.org/event/adam-faucett-t-v-mike/?instance_id=94887
X-SOURCE:WFHB Community Calendar
END:VEVENT
