UID:ai1ec-148332-94899@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Saturday April 18th is Record Store Day 2026! Landlocked will 
 open at 8AM to begin selling the exclusive releases for the day. There wil
 l be a line\, which will be served in the order of the queue. Cash Is King
  and makes the line move faster. Have a list of the items you want to purc
 hase ready. All titles will be behind the counter until the line is gone. 
 Over the years we (Landlocked) have found this method is both fair and san
 e for customers and our employees.12 NOON – 12:30pm:Molly Tuttle is grac
 ing the instore stage on RSD for a solo mini set at 12 NOON. CDs and LPs w
 ill be available to purchase\, and Molly will sign items and meet her fans
  following the performance. Please be respectful of the artist and the que
 ue.Landlocked passed their 20 year milestone last month. To celebrate\, th
 ey are relaunching the awesome Chris Mott design from 2020 with new added 
 flair in new awesome colors. RSD Totes and T-shirts will be available at t
 he shop!
LOCATION:Landlocked Music: 115 S. Walnut St.
