UID:ai1ec-147327-94356@wfhb.org
DESCRIPTION:Presented by Constellation Stage and Screen + Buskirk-Chumley 
 Theater.Calling all dancing queens and super troupers!Experience the magic
  of ABBA’s greatest hits on the big screen in this feel-good movie music
 al about a bride-to-be searching for her real father. Based on the Broadwa
 y musical of the same name\,Mamma Mia!is a high-energy celebration of love
 \, friendship\, and timeless pop classics.Be sure to dress in yourMamma Mi
 a-best\, because we’re kicking off the screening with a costume contest!
  Show off your disco- and island-inspired looks for the chance to win a fa
 bulous prize. Come early to take photos at our photo booth and grab a them
 ed cocktail from the bar.Learn more and find tickets athttps://seeconstell
 ation.org/films/mamma-mia/
LOCATION:Buskirk-Chumley Theater\, 114 E. Kirkwood Ave\, Bloomington
